column1: God puts people in your life for a reason, and removes them from your life for a better reason.
I don't know what tomorrow holds, but I know who holds tomorrow.

Not my will, but Yours. 
God, be done. I need less of me and more of You.

بها يبارك رب الجنود قائلا مبارك شعبي مصر و عمل يدي اشور و ميراثي اسرائيل 

اشعياء 19:25
When everyone else fails you, God won't.
Jesus take the wheel, take it from my hands, because I can't do this on my own, I am letting go, give me one more chance,  save me from this road I am on, Jesus.
Its amazing how God works in the most mysterious ways. :)
“Ask, and it will be given to you; seek, and you will find; knock, and it will be opened to you." Matthew 7:7
I was saved by a blood donor. JESUS
Don't worry or be anxious about tomorrow (Matt 6:34) Because,God is already there.
THOUGHT FOR TODAY..Lord, Thank you for having the patience to deal with me when sometimes I don't even have the patience to deal with myself.
Whatever the world does to me, my security is settled in Christ.
Hears Jesus saying, "In this world you will have trouble.  But take heart..I have overcome the world!" (John 16:33).
Father in Heaven, Thank You for the comfort that comes from knowing You. I rest in Your presence. I find comfort in knowing that You are here.
I will not allow myself to be depressed because I am stronger than that. Keep your head up high and be grateful that the Lord made you of her Creation.

Wonders how I will please the Lord today.  Dear Jesus, move my heart to do Your will.  Make me a blessing in someones life today.<3 

I Love Yu Father. <3
Jesus softly said, "I may never leave you or forsake you,I will be with you to the end".I whisper , "THANK YOU JESUS.I LOVE YOU"

I must keep reminding myself that when satan tries to tear me down I simply point her to the cross and remind her of my Lord who lifts me up. 

Thannk You LORD !

Sometimes I Just Feel Like Giving Up. And Then I Do... I Give It Up To God. (:
Jesus I LOVE YOU !

Mayar Ashraf 
It's Yuur Day !!!! 
Happy Birthdaay My EVERYTHINNGG !! 
Hope Yu Ennjoyy Itt. <3 

I LOVE YOU MRE THAN WORDS CAN EVER TELL. <3
Mayar Ashraf .. We're Moving To London xP <3
